    "description": "<strong>《共鸣：安可》和正式版区别<br>角色：安可3个英雄2个场景，正式版7个英雄和更多的战斗场景<br>难度：安可只能挑战2个难度，正式版每个英雄都有6个难度可挑战<br>曲库：安可的随机曲库收录了7首额外曲目，正式版有20+首额外曲目，且持续不断更新添加</strong><br><br><strong>欢迎加入我们的玩家社群和QQ官方群，请告诉我们对这款游戏的想法和意见。<br>《共鸣》玩家QQ群：103224246<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/e578f0ab9bf6cfbf410833506accc1de.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=276 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/07042317f343167626adc9a24f5e39e6.poster.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/07042317f343167626adc9a24f5e39e6.webm?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/07042317f343167626adc9a24f5e39e6.mp4?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>全新英雄——送葬者子裘来啦。<br>送葬者子裘可以通过召唤和控制怪物的乐魂来协助战斗</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/6d74edbf2840ef9d10aaee1bc183f72b.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=212 /></span><br><strong>连续击中节拍可以累计连奏等级，音乐会变得更丰满，而且还会激活角色更强的性能。<br>新模式——随机曲库模式<br>开启随机曲库模式，使用任意英雄将从二十多首全新曲目中随机播放。感受不一样的战斗节奏！<br>自定义曲目<br>玩家可以自行导入喜欢的曲目到游戏文件夹中，在游戏中切换至——「自定义曲目」模式，即可使用自定义音乐游玩。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/022d93d3115dd1df4481bcbb3dd8a00f.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/0d2504ae67252e0c46aaec0b85946696.poster.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/0d2504ae67252e0c46aaec0b85946696.webm?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/0d2504ae67252e0c46aaec0b85946696.mp4?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>不同的英雄会带来不同的音乐和不同的节奏<br>针对不同的节奏操作，释放出的技能也将完全不同</strong>、<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/bce1200e09c78eb467fe4c948bc62e9a.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/51c7f8d3703b7b2f31f79baac52bec87.poster.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/51c7f8d3703b7b2f31f79baac52bec87.webm?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/51c7f8d3703b7b2f31f79baac52bec87.mp4?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>招募使用不同乐器的音乐家：贝斯手谭佩、吉他手富力吉安、提琴演奏家艾欧莉安等等<br>加入其对应的演奏音色,组成不同的乐队，丰富演奏中的乐曲<br>欣赏不同演奏味道的音乐，感受不同的战斗风格</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/a17a2e154d8745d69dfba9e502b65be0.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/72ae8746fa18c024c4c7c426c3b63785.poster.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/72ae8746fa18c024c4c7c426c3b63785.webm?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/72ae8746fa18c024c4c7c426c3b63785.mp4?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/3cbc708ac5177f04980330cf1a0b8a24.avif?t=1721486110\" width=618 height=184 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/e0d008fd534c9948a4a35dd88d3a8603.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/5cb86881c3151faafde8daa74355bece.poster.avif?t=1721486110\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/5cb86881c3151faafde8daa74355bece.webm?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097340/extras/5cb86881c3151faafde8daa74355bece.mp4?t=1721486110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>随着不断击退虚空怪物，深入故事，探寻角色和世界的真相</strong></strong>",
